Ide prema prostorijama za posadu.
-Je li neko tamo dole?

835
01:43:21,095 --> 01:43:24,264
Riks i Apvort.
-Sranje. Idemo tamo.

836
01:43:24,465 --> 01:43:27,634
Voltere! Oglasi alarm!
Upozori ih!

837
01:43:28,135 --> 01:43:31,438
Pažnja.
Riks i Apvort,

838
01:43:31,638 --> 01:43:34,108
napustite prostorije za posadu smesta.

839
01:43:35,342 --> 01:43:37,044
Riks i Apvort,

840
01:43:37,311 --> 01:43:39,179
napustite...

841
