846
01:45:11,905 --> 01:45:13,607
Ovuda.

847
01:45:21,315 --> 01:45:25,052
Ti, izaberimo teren.
Namamićemo ga kod nas.

848
01:45:25,285 --> 01:45:28,622
Gde?
